section#advanced

    h1 Enjoy it in your own way! Casual or Hardcore. 
    h2 Delve deeper and explore our never-ending paths of global progression.

    p In addition to minigames and "e-toys", Pollux also provides an ellaborated social sphere with its own global progression system.

    .adv-feat(plx-lightbox)
        - var link = "/images/showcase/craft.png" 
        a(href=link)
            img(plx-img src=link)
        h3.title Crafting
        h4.sub Mix, Create, Discover!
        p If you enjoy exploring and poking around with putting things together and see what comes out of it. Our crafting system is one of the richest you'll find. You can craft from recipes, or just experiment with stuff you have in your hands and see what comes out of it!
    
    .adv-feat(plx-lightbox)
        - var link ="/images/showcase/venture.png" 
        a(href=link)
            img(plx-img src=link)
        h1.title Adventure Mode
        h3.subtitle It is back! Better than ever
        p 
            | You asked for it and it is back! The "Venture Forth" minigame from the Hallowinter 2019 event has been upgraded to a full minigame module!
            br
            | Explore different places and landscape to find and collect all sorts of stuff and unveil stories and mysteries from Pollux's universe!

    .adv-feat(plx-lightbox)
        - var link = "/images/showcase/storefront.png" 
        a(href=link)
            img(plx-img src=link)
        h1.title The Marketplace
        h3.subtitle Now everyone can be a merchant
